<h2>Judge Beer ... Get Paid</h2>
<div id="top_ten">
  <h3>Top Ten Reasons You Should Judge at the Brewers&#8217; Cup</h3>
<ol>
  <li value="10"> We need your expertise.</li>
  <li value="9"> Come back and visit with all your friends.</li>
  <li value="8"> Indianapolis is a hopping town.</li>
  <li value="7"> The energy at this competition is palpable.</li>
  <li value="6"> Darn good food and lots of it.</li>
  <li value="5"> BJCP points.</li>
  <li value="4"> We treat our judges well.</li>
  <li value="3"> BJCP points.</li>
  <li value="2"> We pay a small stipend.</li>
  <li value="1"> This competition is a well-oiled machine!</li>
